# [NETMOD](../wg/netmod.html)

## Summary
The NETMOD Working Group met at IETF 120. The session began with working group status updates, followed by progress reports on active WG documents including modules addressing IANA guidelines, YANG packages, schema comparison, and the roadmap for YANG Next / YANG 2.0. The group also discussed several individual proposals covering YANG configuration templates, subtree replacements, normalized forms for string-derived types, library feature comparisons, and YANG schema test coverage tools. Multiple polls were conducted during the session to gauge consensus on adopting new work.

